Comment: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:02.07,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Good morning, low-class hot spring inn.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.07,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Good morning,
Comment: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,staff of the low-class hot spring inn.
Comment: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.70,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi?
Comment: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.12,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,You're supposed to greet\N your customers with "Welcome!"
Comment: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.04,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,This is one of the basic principles of running an inn!
Comment: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Comment: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.51,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Takako!
Comment: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.80,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming by so early!
Comment: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.68,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I've already had to teach your staff a lesson.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.72,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Forget about them.
Comment: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.89,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Come, it's this way!
Comment: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.40,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'll include it in my consulting fee.
Comment: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.85,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Of course!
Comment: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.24,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I really want to clean her up too.
Comment: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.57,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that!
Comment: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.45,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We have a guest, Mom.
Comment: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Kawajiri Takako, Management Consultant.
Comment: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.00,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,"Madam Manager."
Comment: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Right, Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.46,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Come on, she came to say hello.
Comment: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.42,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling very well.
Comment: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.88,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But you were feeling fine yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.76,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,But not this morning.
Comment: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.43,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Please wait, Takako!
Comment: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We were in the middle of making breakfast here.
Comment: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.90,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,And we're in the middle of clean—
Comment: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.69,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Listen up, this is very important since
Comment: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's related to the Kissui Inn's future!
Comment: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.32,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Now, if you will, Ms. Kawajiri.
Comment: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.99,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Good morning, ladies and gentlemen.
Comment: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:32.50,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,As you may know, I'm Kawajiri\N Takako, a management consultant.
Comment: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.25,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'm here to revitalize this Inn.
Comment: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.29,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you!
Comment: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.59,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,I know.
Comment: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.79,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I know.
Comment: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Does she drop by often?
Comment: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.38,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,About once a month.
Comment: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:46.80,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Well, the radical change I'm presenting to you today
Comment: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is regarding the waitresses.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.43,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,We're going back to the kitchen.
Comment: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.35,Default,A,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Comment: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.94,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,No fair!
Comment: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.77,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,We had our turn last month, remember?
Comment: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.73,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Comment: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.78,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,The plan I brought today is perfect!
Comment: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.07,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Listen closely,
Comment: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to choose a new\N design for the waitresses' uniforms!
Comment: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.66,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What are they?
Comment: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.04,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn will continue to remain in the past
Comment: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if you keep wearing those old-fashioned uniforms.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:19.67,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,If we improve the inn's image with the latest fashion trends,
Comment: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.34,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,then the customers will be even more satisfied!
Comment: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.55,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,No way.
Comment: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.97,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Comment: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.63,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than wear that...
Comment: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I don't think that waitresses at a hot spring inn
Comment: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,should be wearing these.
Comment: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.31,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,That's what's we call a "fixed idea".
Comment: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.98,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,"Standing pools gather filth!"
Comment: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.31,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Ever heard of that phrase before?
Comment: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:42.44,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Can't you feel the stagnant\N atmosphere of this moldy inn?!
Comment: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.57,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Well, the futons {\i1}are{\i0} a little moldy...
Comment: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.82,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,O-Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.62,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,And that's why we need to try this!
Comment: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.16,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Challenge! Venture!
Comment: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.79,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Nothing venture, nothing win!
Comment: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.96,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Keep those words in mind!
Comment: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Comment: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.29,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Challenge...
Comment: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Could this... possibly be a good idea?
Comment: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.59,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.43,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,That's it!
Comment: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.80,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,It's a very good idea!
Comment: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.81,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Comment: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.35,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Comment: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Time for work! Work!
