Comment: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.20,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Comment: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.17,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Stunningly gorgeous.
Comment: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.84,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,That looks great on you.
Comment: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Are you sure this counts as a "challenge"?
Comment: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:46.84,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.30,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,It's a challenge.
Comment: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.39,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But I don't want a challenge...
Comment: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.85,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,It'll be over soon.
Comment: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.27,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Now, let's find some customers who like this kind of fashion.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.93,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If I recall...
