Comment: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.84,Default,Cust,0,0,0,,Hello.
Comment: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.01,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Comment: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.72,Default,Cust,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Comment: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,He's surprised,
Comment: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,or maybe he's touched?
Comment: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Maybe this will be a success after all!
Comment: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.19,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Wait, wasn't Mr. Tachibana coming with his...
