Comment: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.25,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Me?
Comment: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.71,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But I'm not!
Comment: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?!
Comment: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.42,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore!
Comment: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.76,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Our deepest apologies.
Comment: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.14,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Our deepest apologies.
Comment: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.89,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Comment: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.52,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You probably enjoyed it, didn't you?
Comment: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:30.65,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,No, that's not—
Comment: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.74,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,We're really sorry!
Comment: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That was a complete failure, wasn't it?
Comment: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.67,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,That's why I refused to do it in the beginning...
Comment: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.01,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Your forehead is red, Nakochi.
Comment: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.68,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Comment: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I guess we chose the wrong design...
