Comment: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.20,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Cosplay?
Comment: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.24,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I guess inns that aren't doing so well
Comment: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,really do have to try a lot of new things.
Comment: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're just going to say that right to my face?
Comment: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.29,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I'm just impressed!
Comment: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.87,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,You're all so hard-working and full of spirit!
Comment: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.71,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,That's so admirable...
Comment: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:34.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But the biggest problem is that our\N hard work doesn't actually get us anywhere.
