Comment: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.95,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I guess not all challenges are rewarded.
Comment: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.80,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.92,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Comment: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.01,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I get yelled at whenever I'm late!
Comment: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.43,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Me too!
Comment: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.97,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Me three!
Comment: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.47,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I don't care about you.
Comment: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That kind of hurts...
Comment: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We won't be yelled at for coming back at this hour, right?
Comment: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Are the kitchen shifts different from ours?
Comment: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.57,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Minchi told me that she wants to learn how to
Comment: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,make the dinner from scratch.
Comment: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.45,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Comment: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.74,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Takako, please don't go!
Comment: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.99,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,If you don't need my consultations,
Comment: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no need for me to be here.
Comment: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.58,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,No one said that you weren't needed here!
Comment: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Right, Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.96,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,We don't need her.
Comment: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But Mom!
Comment: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.17,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,"Madam Manager."
Comment: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wait, stop!
Comment: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:55.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Takako!
Comment: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Comment: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.59,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.52,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,He seems a bit bummed out.
Comment: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Should we say something to him?
Comment: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.81,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Comment: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.52,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You two...
Comment: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.23,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Comment: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.03,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,W-We'll be getting to work immediately!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi sure is quick-witted.
Comment: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:20.90,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,And you?
Comment: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Right away, Ma'am.
Comment: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:52.64,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,So that consultant majored in management in college
Comment: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.44,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,and even went to graduate school?
Comment: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.73,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,That's what they say.
Comment: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.82,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Apparently, the young master met her in college.
Comment: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.53,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I do understand why he's panicking though.
Comment: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:05.03,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Our inn isn't doing well at all.
Comment: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.74,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Comment: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.45,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,We haven't been getting many\N customers for quite some time now.
Comment: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.96,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's why we need to try new things.
Comment: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.75,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But I don't want to dress up like that again.
Comment: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.38,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'd wear something else, Nakochi?
Comment: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.93,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.76,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Well, it's not our place to worry about it.
Comment: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.97,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I'd rather not wear stuff like that though.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.31,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Comment: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.15,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,See you!
Comment: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.47,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Comment: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,N-Nothing!
Comment: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.09,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What {\i1}do{\i0} I want?
Comment: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You don't seem to be very cheerful.
Comment: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.31,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is it because Madam Manager yelled at you?
Comment: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:19.31,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Well, both Tomoe and Nakochi\N didn't like the uniforms either...
Comment: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.11,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Everyone says things like that.
Comment: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:30.12,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I understand that I'm being a tad unreasonable,
Comment: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.66,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,but everything I do is for the sake of this inn.
Comment: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.71,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But even then, Mom...
Comment: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Even if a plan fails...
Comment: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better than not trying at all!
Comment: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.47,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.85,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,"Cheer up!"
Comment: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.27,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm sure things will work out in the end!
Comment: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.98,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sis... Satsuki?
Comment: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.15,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,My mom?
Comment: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.99,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Whenever I felt down,
Comment: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that's how she used to cheer me up.
Comment: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Telling you to cheer up\N without giving you a reason to, right?
Comment: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly that.
Comment: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.13,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's awful, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.13,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,she's your mother.
Comment: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.22,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,And?
Comment: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:36.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So I was thinking that there might be\N something that even I can do for the Inn.
Comment: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.98,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Like?
Comment: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.90,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What do you say to cosplaying with us, Minchi?
Comment: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.52,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense.
Comment: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.32,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You might be popular with the customers.
Comment: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Tooru would definitely enjoy it.
Comment: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.70,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Shut up and die!
Comment: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.74,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I thought we agreed not to—
Comment: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.66,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Balut!
Comment: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.95,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Good night.
Comment: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I need to find something I can do...
Comment: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.89,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,In the current situation, I just can't be proud
Comment: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of this 20,000 yen.
Comment: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:25.11,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You came to bother me this early in\N the morning about that shady woman?
Comment: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's just that I understand how the young master feels.
Comment: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.36,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,If the Kissui Inn goes out of business
Comment: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,without us trying anything—
Comment: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.45,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Why would this place go out of business?
Comment: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.12,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Who said anything like that?
Comment: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.46,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Th-That's just a small part of it!
Comment: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.42,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,No, it isn't.
Comment: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:49.59,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think it's a good idea to try something new!
Comment: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.63,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Like what?
Comment: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.97,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Like...
Comment: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Lengthening the slit in the Chinese dresses?
Comment: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But if this place goes out of business,
Comment: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have nowhere else to go!
Comment: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.86,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,If you mention us going out of business again,
Comment: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're fired.
Comment: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.36,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Then, "declining"?
Comment: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.86,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,We've been declining for a while,
Comment: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't really care.
Comment: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:13.03,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.00,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:35.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Sorry, Beanman, but I was in the\N middle of a debate with Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.05,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Business has been bad for a while.
Comment: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,For a while?
Comment: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.73,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Madam Manager knows that very well.
Comment: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if she realizes this, why doesn't she do\N something to try and make things better?
Comment: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.03,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I do know that the young master's\N ideas aren't exactly the brightest, but...
Comment: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What is...
Comment: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,W-Wow!
Comment: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I never knew this room existed!
Comment: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,This one's so pretty!
Comment: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.85,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So is this one!
Comment: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,And this one's chic!
Comment: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Did Madam Manager make all of these?
Comment: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:34.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Some of these are old, but they aren't damaged at all.
Comment: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:36.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Are you taking care of them?
Comment: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.11,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Comment: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh!
Comment: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.12,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Beanman?
Comment: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi!
Comment: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You look so cute, Nakochi!
Comment: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.04,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,So do you, Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:51.92,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Really?!
Comment: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.59,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.26,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Isn't this one pretty?
Comment: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:06.02,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,What on earth are you two wearing?
Comment: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.73,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:10.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,How do we look?
Comment: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.61,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,How did you find those?
Comment: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.32,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's time for a challenge!
Comment: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.08,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What on earth...
Comment: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.88,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I've finished cleaning the entrance!
Comment: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.72,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Jiro—
Comment: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.35,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Aren't those...
Comment: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.69,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Wow!
Comment: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.36,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Your clothes are so pretty!
Comment: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.03,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Can I touch them?
Comment: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Comment: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.65,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,It's so soft, Mom!
Comment: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.95,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow!
Comment: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.95,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Madam Manager was wearing this\N too the very first time I stayed here.
Comment: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.67,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Really? How long ago was that?
Comment: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.84,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Long before you were born, I bet.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.84,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow...
Comment: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.96,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,She was really pretty, I tell you. {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you so early in the morning.
Comment: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.47,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What? Well, well.
Comment: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,This does bring back some old memories.
Comment: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.18,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I must admit it's rather embarrassing.
Comment: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.35,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But why?
Comment: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You're the one who designed this in the first place.
Comment: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.32,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I was?
Comment: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:38.69,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, you were\N trying to come up with "something new",
Comment: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.11,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,and that made your husband angry with you.
Comment: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wasn't it something like that?
Comment: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.45,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I really can't remember...
Comment: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.49,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,It was so long ago.
Comment: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:51.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Come on, you're not old\N enough to start forgetting things yet!
Comment: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Well then, see you.
Comment: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.84,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,We hope to see you again.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.30,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\rAlternative}Thank you very much. {\r}Thank you very much!
Comment: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,And so the Inn's past is revealed.
Comment: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.89,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Comment: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.94,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,What was with that bow?
Comment: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.23,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.61,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You looked like a feeding rooster.
Comment: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.28,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,A bow like that insults the customer.
Comment: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Ma'am!
Comment: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.66,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, Madam Manager, I need\N to talk to you about something.
Comment: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.53,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You still haven't had enough?
Comment: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.45,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Just hear me out, Mom!
Comment: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.16,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,"Madam Manager!"
Comment: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:31.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Madam Manager, this one will work out for sure!
Comment: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Comment: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:53.52,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we get more\N customers from what we did this morning,
Comment: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.19,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,but maybe things don't work out that easily.
Comment: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.61,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,We're going to be late! We're going to be late!
Comment: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.94,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Where's Minchi?
Comment: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.15,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,You're so slow!
Comment: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Wait, Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.87,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Trust me, the next one will work out!
Comment: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.12,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. I have an even better idea.
Comment: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But doing something will at least cause something else to happen.
Comment: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:34.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I don't know whether it's\N better for the Inn to change or not,
Comment: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:38.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,but as long as we're doing {\i1}something{\i0}, it's good.
Comment: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Those are my thoughts.
Comment: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:33.72,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Hell if I know.
Comment: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.60,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's worth continuing this job.
Comment: 1,0:23:38.56,0:23:41.39,Default,Girl3,0,0,0,,Okay, my waitress life is officially over!
